{"id":232824392,"title":"A7iii /Tamron 28-75 選擇","content":"版上各位前輩 大家好\n小弟攝影菜雞 目前是使用A72+kit\n90%都是以拍攝人像為主\n現在剛好手上有大概兩萬多的預算\n想請問各位前輩\n是該賣掉A72 然後升級二手A73？\n還是該升級鏡頭繼續用A72？\n\n目前遇到最大的瓶頸在於夜晚或是光線不足的時候 對焦速度太慢 且噪點常常蠻爆的 再來就是A72沒有眼控 常常在拍完後製時才發現焦點不在自己所設想的位置上 所以才萌生了升級A73的想法 但又考慮到之前某位前輩說的 升級相機只是一時爽感而已 沒法使你的照片變得更好 因此就在機身與鏡頭間猶豫\n\n麻煩各位前輩 為小弟解惑了 感謝各位\n\n在此附上之前拍的一些拙作\n方便各位前輩給小弟建議 傷眼的話 非常抱歉\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34a234ce-1061-43b8-bf0b-0ae4764f8ae4/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/85c2419c-be06-45c8-ae9f-925f86c8e0c9/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/65bb98f0-515e-4073-b969-3163c7a98e81/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6bd6e638-f4b1-4d7d-bcb6-539e0ff5e5cb/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e33ca7f1-d8b7-4071-928a-f0d58f015af6/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"版上各位前輩 大家好，小弟攝影菜雞 目前是使用A72+kit，90%都是以拍攝人像為主，現在剛好手上有大概兩萬多的預算，想請問各位前輩，是該賣掉A72 然後升級二手A73？還是該升級鏡頭繼續用A72？","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-04T11:57:35.150Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-04T23:05:58.576Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["相機","攝影器材"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"16.9_x","department":"gtfo_x","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/34a234ce-1061-43b8-bf0b-0ae4764f8ae4/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/85c2419c-be06-45c8-ae9f-925f86c8e0c9/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/65bb98f0-515e-4073-b969-3163c7a98e81/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6bd6e638-f4b1-4d7d-